e; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">世界首创用&ldquo;水&rdquo;阻击眼疾病！</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"line-height: 54px;\">神秘效果源于九千多年前原生态达古冰川泉水！</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\"><span style=\"background-color: #cccccc;\">细胞生态健康水核心四大亮点</span></span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0pt 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: -36pt; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 36pt; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">（1）<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">唯一性</span>：水源地采自位于黑水县芦花镇境内的达古冰川，每一滴都来自青藏高原海拔3800-5100米的达古冰川，经中国地震局国家地质研究所测定，水龄为9610年。经优化&ldquo;核磁干预&rdquo;技术处理，获得国家发明专利技术产品，专利号：201010569535.2</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: -36pt; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 36pt; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">（2）<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">创新与高度安全环保性</span>：非药物的&ldquo;水&rdquo;阻击和清除疾病的新方式通过&ldquo;水&rdquo;遏制脱水性过氧化，清除有害自由基对细胞的损伤。无任何药物、激素、防腐剂、氧化剂、动植物等成分，不会带来毒副作用和过敏。高度安全卫生、深入内在的绿色环保！</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: -36pt; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 36pt; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">（3）<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">高效性</span>：使用10分钟显效，绝大部分都在2-3月达到理想好效果。</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: -36pt; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 36pt; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">（4）<span style=\"background-color: #ffff00;\">权威性</span>：目前已获八大国际权威机构鉴证。</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: -36pt; margin: 0pt 0px 0pt 36pt; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\"><strong></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">细胞生态护眼水</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: none; background-color: #ffffff; text-indent: 0px; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; white-space: normal; orphans: 2; letter-spacing: normal; color: #404040; word-break: break-all; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; padding: 0px;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-family: \'microsoft yahei\';\"><span style=\"color: #38761d;\">绝大多数眼疾病是因过度用眼和不良用眼引起的脱水性过氧化导致的有害自由基对眼睛的伤害。眼疾病防治、眼机能退化治理、眼健康保护的根本应从阻击与遏制脱水性过氧化，抑制清除有害自由基做起。</span></span></span></strong></p>\r\n<p style=\"widows: 2; text-transform: n